Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.47,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\pos(580,280)}旅途的天空的盡頭的紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.33,0:24:08.50,NEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颱風幽靈 今天的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:28.30,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こぼれそうな夢の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:33.97,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}よろこびを探す世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:44.95,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君はどんな輝きで　明日へと跳ぶの？　教えてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:50.68,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}声になった未来の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:56.22,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}始まりの my melody 聞こえた？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:01:02.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm READY！ 空が青く高くて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:07.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}涙ぐんだ今を忘れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:13.17,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ひたすら進もうと誓うから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:17.22,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}分かりあった瞬間は大切な
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:20.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:20.95,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an7}ずっと一緒に　君と一緒に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:23.61,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑っていればいいね多分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.69,0:01:26.36,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっと一緒だ　君と一緒で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:29.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在の鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:35.17,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Are you READY？ だから今を信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:40.07,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誇らしくなるね君の想い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:46.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}やたらに眩しいよその笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:50.37,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}向かいあって本心は負けないと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:53.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop mind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:28.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}灑落著夢的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:33.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是找尋著喜悅的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:44.95,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你帶著怎樣的光芒 向著明日起航 告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:56.22,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傾聽憧憬著未來的心跳 那是我邁向明天的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:01:02.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm READY! 無垠的天空湛藍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:07.31,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不要忘記今天的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:13.17,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約定好一起大步向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:17.22,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心靈相通的瞬間 是如此珍重的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:20.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:20.95,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}想要一直在一起 同你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:23.61,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要有微笑就別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.69,0:01:26.36,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在一起 和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:29.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊握通向明天的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:35.17,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Are you READY? 所以我相信現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:40.07,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的思念讓我自豪無比
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:46.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的笑臉是那麼的光彩奪目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:50.37,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直面真心就不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:53.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:44.23,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}急に黙り込んで　君は手を繋いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:49.20,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}茜空に消えてく今日を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:54.26,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}見送る長いかげぼうし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.63,0:22:59.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}放課後は永遠みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.26,0:23:03.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}サヨナラをごまかしてたね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.02,0:23:14.04,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}だけど心は旅立ちの予感を知ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.93,0:23:20.46,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}果てしない未来への
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.63,0:23:25.12,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}躊躇いを隠して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.49,0:23:33.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}微笑む君の夢が眩しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.84,0:23:39.49,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あと少しの季節を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:44.29,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}惜しむようにはしゃいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:53.38,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明日への帰り道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:44.23,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}突然沉默不語的你 靜靜地把我的手握起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:49.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}漸漸延向地平線的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:54.26,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}訴說著一天又隨著夕陽沉去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.63,0:22:59.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你說放學後的時光就像永恆一樣漫長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.26,0:23:03.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}把離別的那一刻深藏心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.02,0:23:14.04,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}但是彼此卻都深知即將各自啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.93,0:23:25.12,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}掩飾著對未知旅途的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.49,0:23:33.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}微笑著的你 夢想是那樣的絢麗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.84,0:23:39.49,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}讓我們珍惜這所剩無幾的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:44.29,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}盡情歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:53.38,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}然後踏上通往明天的歸程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.88,0:00:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.99,0:00:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.93,0:00:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  你是這個島上的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你救了我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你們這群外地人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜  你走的太快了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是回海裏去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去旅店放好行李再說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真嚇人啊  夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在為剛才的事生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這沒辦法吧  我們就是外地人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到很多曬著的潛水服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海裏穿的那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說正在接受體驗潛水的報名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？ 好啊好啊  潛水去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和魚兒一起嬉戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還能見到海龜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  離旅店還很遠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看  應該在十字路的對面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴聲？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴聲？  午休時間響的那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在進行社團活動  去吧  凜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  只要說是來參觀的就沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季也很想看看這裏是個什麼樣的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「誒」什麼啊  你要轉學到這裏來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管她  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去優香你就去不成海邊了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  難得來一次的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（注：おじゃりやれ，八丈岛地区方言）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸  胸  胸部…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要盯著看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離山好近  不錯  不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雙胞胎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是分身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  澡堂已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:03:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你變成女孩子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你們見到小晴了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晴？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的雙胞胎妹妹小晴  沖山小晴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是姐姐的沖山千晴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  原來是雙胞胎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千晴小姐是高中生嗎  我們初二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一樣大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣大…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始努力就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是從本島的哪兒來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜岡的下田你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下田？  我知道  下田的水越醫生你們認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的話早點說就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您認識我的爸爸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兒的人大家都認識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近的診所停業了  水越醫生能來真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,號外  號外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  是千啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（收件箱  標題：群發！ 大家~！新來的醫生的女兒來這座島上玩了~）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晴  你在啊  過來幫一下忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上泡澡最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你搓背
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  新來的醫生的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們家的孩子一樣大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季不用搬家也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  紗季小姐在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:05:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是住在這附近的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千晴發郵件給我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來給你做嚮導吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季小姐  紗季小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面有聽到聲音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要泡暈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜你泡暈了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季小姐  紗季小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她為什麼要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家有好好打招呼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真有人氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又不是給人參觀的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季你先藏好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起打擾到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴巾我放在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是旅店的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒關繫了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你泡暈了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你先快點出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是小晴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能沉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜？ 咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛好像聽到彭的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我是）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（紗季）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的看不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  應該不會是神石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因為那塊石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  它是神石的親戚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親戚是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把這種東西放在澡堂裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蟲子出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:09:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季沒和你們在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間  她在房間睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晴  小晴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為被偷窺了  於是就不由自主地把他…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晴是女孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們先退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來她們是雙胞胎姐妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季  在這裏嗎  在這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的事都由我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們中誰是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:09:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東西拿得起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（接下來該怎麼辦？）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把紗季變回原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既看不見又聽不到  太不方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什麼時候能變回原樣  你們三個先去海邊玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是四個人一起就沒意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我們不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個  我說紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一絲不掛的居然一點都不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味  天婦羅太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一會兒老闆娘她們會來鋪床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼解釋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去廁所了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（還變不回原樣 真是抱歉）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  沒事  在回去之前變回來就行了  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果變不回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說什麼如果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多星星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季還沒變回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼她會消失呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為神石的親戚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問的不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她太害羞了  之類的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小晴是女的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也該變回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻血也不流了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不是這個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季一直在煩惱著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時候讓你轉校真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你會喜歡那個島
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水越醫生能來真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你們這些外地人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在看這裏的學校時也有點奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得她是不想搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她完全沒那麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季是不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那就無能為力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季不會搬家的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你向神石許願了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在來這裏之前我和她說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去說服叔叔  讓紗季不搬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對她說了那種話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種話？ 你們不希望她留下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不想她搬啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們還只是中學生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能跟著父母走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就住在我家就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多一個人出來可是很辛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家有個姐姐  所以很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她只在休息日才住家裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季要在你們家住多久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海的媽媽人很好  所以可能會答應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大樹也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海  這個世界上沒辦法的事情還是有的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會很寂寞  但又不是這輩子都見不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想見她的話就可以去見她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說得這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從下田到這裏用了多少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開窗戶也再也看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是不同空間了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使相隔兩地  友情是不會結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼不可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們三個人就花上一天時間來看她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說因為太遠了夏海就不來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就說聲「會發郵件的」 然後兩個人就斷絕聯繫了  這也是常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會發的  一定會發的  還會打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒關繫了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼早就要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起做她們的嚮導…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別遷怒於紗季她們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在刷牙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  紗季呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  她去散步了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  我還想帶她到處看看的說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龜常出沒的地方  還有這個島最大的土特產店
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土特產
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（去吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我也去就沒問題了吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好多船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是捕飛魚和金目鯛的船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要  搖得好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  妨礙您工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子就別和我客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能帶得回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫宅急便送回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個就附贈給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水越醫生能吃魚幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.53,0:16:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它看得見你？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由自主地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在錄像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得好  來得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆  她不是紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  你的爸爸真的很了不起  這樣大家就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季的爸爸好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個島的人都很友善  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晴不那樣說話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千晴  紗季的爸爸在哪家醫院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:17:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們家附近有個診所  他就在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,診所？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  因為有點遠我們坐出租車去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好簡潔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜  要坐坐看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰醫生的桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千晴  別讓她們進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是外人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏本來是一位老爺爺醫生的診所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為身體不太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很快就要去住在本土的孫子家住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為要來新的傢伙要來  所以沒法繼續做醫生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生明明說他還能幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千晴也聽到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生一直這樣說著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮上的人的病讓我來看  他會一直在這個島上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是醫生他在勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.47,0:18:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體已經受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是因為那個約定  所以不想離開這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後有一天  接到一個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是以前的學生打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是醫生終於露出了笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他的話  是水越君的話  這裏就能交給他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我出生前他就一直在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳  學習也都是他教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼千晴和大家能無動於衷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和醫生說再見  大家都很傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和醫生也很傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的不只是小晴一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的醫生是個好醫生就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的  他一定是個好醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我們朋友的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後能再去一個地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是島上的人才知道的特別的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季要在這裏生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你從哪裏冒出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季  你衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨身帶著衣服真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季  我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.56,0:20:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼練習打招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是凜前輩的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從轉校這個角度來講
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是常有的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的招呼是非常重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是水越紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太短了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候我會多說一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛  不應該拍手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖山同學  請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼叫  叫我小晴就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.34,0:21:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一次真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.78,0:21:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始計劃接下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離搬家已經沒多少時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女易老  快去創造回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季竟然會贊同我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為要去創造回憶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.37,0:22:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季想去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏都行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.20,0:22:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.14,0:23:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.27,0:23:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是聽說颱風要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.71,0:24:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是這麼好的天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.91,0:24:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來之前也有一次颱風來了之後好像發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.14,0:24:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集  夏色奇跡  第十話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颱風幽靈  今天的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.74,0:24:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺突然渾身發冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
